com.radaee.util

Class RadaeePluginCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.radaee.util.RadaeePluginCallback

  • public class RadaeePluginCallback
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to manage callbacks between PDF viewer, and calling class. Your class should implement PDFReaderListener to receive its events.
